<h1>侠</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">xiá</span><span class=alesi>(xia2)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 侠 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 侠</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/chivalrous" style="color:black;">chivalrous</a> <a href="/dictionary/person" style="color:black;">person</a>; <a href="/dictionary/knight" style="color:black;">knight</a>-errant</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 8<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 8 strokes: <a href="/character/的" title="de: possessive, adjectival suffix">的</a>, <a href="/character/和" title="he2: harmony, peace; peaceful, calm">和</a>, <a href="/character/国" title="guo2: nation, country, nation-state">国</a>, <a href="/character/到" title="dao4: go to, arrive, been to">到</a>, <a href="/character/所" title="suo3: place, location; numerary adjunct">所</a>, <a href="/character/事" title="shi4: affair, matter, business; to serve; accident, incident">事</a>, <a href="/character/经" title="jing1: classic works; pass through">经</a>, <a href="/character/法" title="fa3: law, rule, regulation, statute; France, French">法</a>, <a href="/character/学" title="xue2: learning, knowledge; school">学</a>, <a href="/character/现" title="xian4: appear, manifest, become visible">现</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/人" title="Kangxi radical 9">人</a>&nbsp;9.6</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 6 <br><small>Other HSK 6 characters: <a href="/character/袭" title="xi2: raid, attack; inherit">袭</a>, <a href="/character/侧" title="ce4: side; incline, slant, lean">侧</a>, <a href="/character/债" title="zhai4: debt, loan, liabilities">债</a>, <a href="/character/融" title="rong2: melt, fuse; blend, harmonize">融</a>, <a href="/character/偏" title="pian1: inclined one side; slanting">偏</a>, <a href="/character/夺" title="duo2: take by force, rob, snatch">夺</a>, <a href="/character/援" title="yuan2: aid, assist; lead; cite">援</a>, <a href="/character/纵" title="zong4: indulge in, give free reign to">纵</a>, <a href="/character/瓦" title="wa3: tile; earthenware pottery; girl">瓦</a>, <a href="/character/障" title="zhang4: separate; shield; barricade">障</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/